{"tid":639058,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"59歲男跑手暈倒危殆","createTime":"2018-04-23T08:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T08:16:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"02a96b8b350e151e1fa78676787d7dabaa440d12","tid":639058,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:16:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180423/20369830?_ga=2.16461750.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180423%2F20369830%3F_ga%3D2.16461750.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=PCppDMVJxsBZWbxFIMycxzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=a3f31161\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180423%2F20369830%3F_ga%3D2.16461750.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=bc49c813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180423/20369830?_ga=2.16461750.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n59歲男跑手暈倒危殆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180423/large/a0604a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180423%2Flarge%2Fa0604a.gif&h=f95e74a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■涉事長跑比賽為Calbee迎「豐」跑，官網介紹主要為香港職業發展服務處推行非政府資助就業支援計劃籌款。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】大埔科學園昨早舉行長跑賽，一名59歲男跑手在比賽途中，突然不支暈倒，同行友人發現報警，事主經送院搶救後，情況危殆，警方正了解事主是否因身體隱疾病發命危。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留醫深切治療部<br />\n<br />\n據悉，涉事長跑比賽為Calbee迎「豐」跑，官網介紹主要為香港職業發展服務處推行非政府資助就業支援計劃籌款，協助更生人士、少數族裔人士及新來港婦女等弱勢社群。活動昨早8時起開始，分1、3及10公里賽事。59歲姓譚男跑手由科學園出發，昨早9時許跑至創新路近大王爺廟對開時突然不適暈倒地上，同行的48歲姓郭男友人見狀立即報警。<br />\n<br />\n救護車其後到場將傷者送往大埔那打素醫院治理，經搶救後目前情況危殆，留醫深切治療病房接受觀察。警方經調查後認為事件無可疑，聯絡其親友到醫院，了解事主是否有患病紀錄，導致突然病發。<br />\n<br />\n■記者莫家文  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n中三學生自覺最不幸福<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n一家三口撞車　父命危"},{"pid":"4b19bcb08c903ab1e63d9a6d81ecedacfbc73b87","tid":639058,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:16:58.000Z","msg":"樓主泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/161650_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F161650_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=9b82a6a4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}